-L%C3%BD-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/%E1%BB%A8c-Mai-Xuy%C3%AAn-k%C3%BD-t%E1%BA%B7ng-hi%E1%BB%87u-Phan-Mai-Xuy%C3%AAn-th%E1%BB%83/poem-5pJi4WCR7RSl4fMec_kAYg">Ức Mai Xuyên ký tặng hiệu Phan Mai Xuyên thể - 憶梅川寄贈傚潘梅川體</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tuy-L%C3%BD-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-B6iyJCR5kCh5mPMgMOCH1Q">Tuy Lý Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/Xu%C3%A2n-du/poem-rxhtjXgrcffJs8Oqy1gTNQ">Xuân du - 春遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/author-0k6qEpgf02Latsw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
